  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2557480/extras/82affd239f73349d9a49d48f1ca3ce80.avif?t=1747846581\" width=650 height=93 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2557480/extras/5d3a9b3e4b6c5c43a6b340b43761a657.poster.avif?t=1747846581\" width=560 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2557480/extras/5d3a9b3e4b6c5c43a6b340b43761a657.webm?t=1747846581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2557480/extras/5d3a9b3e4b6c5c43a6b340b43761a657.mp4?t=1747846581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A sophisticated <strong>malware</strong> created with a sole objective: bypass the defenses of malfunctioning computer systems by <strong>erasing</strong> their cyberspace, in order to reset them to their default state and bring them back to life again. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now it's time for you to take on a <strong>new job</strong>, in a <strong>new system</strong>. Nothing more than just the same old <strong>routine</strong>... probably. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2557480/extras/45d1a3fd22c032c4671057d7aa837978.avif?t=1747846581\" width=650 height=93 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2557480/extras/fe5064430aac91341d3b07f6b3a15208.poster.avif?t=1747846581\" width=560 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2557480/extras/fe5064430aac91341d3b07f6b3a15208.webm?t=1747846581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2557480/extras/fe5064430aac91341d3b07f6b3a15208.mp4?t=1747846581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies are <strong>fragile</strong> and can be erased in <strong>one single hit</strong>, but <strong>so are you</strong>, malware; you must <strong>wipe out</strong> every single defences in an area, in order to proceed to the next one. If you fail, iterate and <strong>try again</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2557480/extras/9ec51419cef9f9930f80b705481644d1.avif?t=1747846581\" width=650 height=93 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2557480/extras/486dc3ad7661a519bbb1f5f09cba6505.poster.avif?t=1747846581\" width=560 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2557480/extras/486dc3ad7661a519bbb1f5f09cba6505.webm?t=1747846581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2557480/extras/486dc3ad7661a519bbb1f5f09cba6505.mp4?t=1747846581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are equipped with various <strong>abilities</strong> (or functions, if you prefer); a good malware knows how to use <strong>each tool</strong> at its disposal, to be as <strong>efficient</strong> as possible during <strong>combat</strong>. Jump, dodge attacks, deflect bullets, throw your trusty scythe. Do everything in your power to <strong>complete your tasks</strong>.</p>",
